Tools for validating OSM public transport relations in Berlin

If you haven't installed mako and protobuf yet (in Debian Wheezy):
apt-get install python-mako python-protobuf

Download OSM data for Berlin from geofabrik.de:
wget http://download.geofabrik.de/osm/europe/germany/berlin.osm.pbf

Start validation/overview script:
./validate.py berlin.osm.pbf template.tpl berlin.htm


This stuff might change soon... currently everything is work in progress.

